data.message:
Operation #Lovedrive3 can't just stop with this season of giving. Let's make it a season of giving all year round. Taking care of our brothers and sisters who are in need. Not my words, but His. Hold me accountable.

10 Give generously to them and do so without a grudging heart; then because of this the Lord your God will bless you in all your work and in everything you put your hand to. 11 There will always be poor people in the land. Therefore I command you to be openhanded toward your fellow Israelites who are poor and needy in your land.
El Paso Lookout. The love can't be stopped...Our younger generations being exposed to a spirit of generosity, of love, and of unity. Together we stand in love:)
Operation #Lovedrive3 about to go down. In T Minus 16 minutes!! Live feed!...Sort of lol
Don't forget your christmas sweatas ya filthy animals! :)
I'm just trying to give some LOOOVE away!💜
Hay folks :) So tomorrow you can bring a POP Top entree of any kind if you don't want to get Chef Boyardee. As long as it's an easy open :]
Can't wait to brighten someone's day this holiday season ❤️
I think we should wear Tacky Christmas Sweaters for Operation #Lovedrive3 !! Don't Forget your POP TOP entree too.  The end product will look a little something like this

Operation #Lovedrive3 is all about spreading love to people around us who are in need. The simple act of feeding someone and sharing an encouraging word   can go further in someones life than you would think. Make a LoveMeal and post it the week of December 14th! #Lovedrive3 @domo2214 -IG
